'''林力仁''' （{{bd|1990年|6月16日|catIdx=L}}）是臺灣職業籃球運動員，主打[[得分後衛|後衛]]位置，現效力於[[P._LEAGUE+|P. LEAGUE+]][[新北國王|新北國王]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=杜奕君 |title=林力仁長大了！　身兼教練盼重燃SBL鬥魂 |url=https://sports.ettoday.net/news/819243 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |work=ETtoday運動雲 |date=2016-11-27 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130174033/https://sports.ettoday.net/news/819243 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=古硯偉 |title=菜鳥教練初體驗 林力仁HBL、SBL兩頭燒 |url=https://video.udn.com/news/588890 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |work=聯合影音網 |date=2016-11-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=曾思儒 |title=籃球／天王盃鬥牛賽 林力仁展神射工夫 |url=https://video.udn.com/news/550055 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |work=聯合影音網 |date=2016-08-27 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130180740/https://video.udn.com/news/550055 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=林力仁 |url=https://www.yulon.com.tw/player/%E6%9E%97%E5%8A%9B%E4%BB%81/ |website=裕隆納智捷 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204164755/https://www.yulon.com.tw/player/%e6%9e%97%e5%8a%9b%e4%bb%81/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=林建嘉 |title=籃球／攻城獅出師不利  林力仁腿傷將缺陣6到8周 |url=https://www.nownews.com/news/5050036 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |work=NOWnews 今日新聞 |date=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129062710/https://www.nownews.com/news/5050036 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黃美珠 |title=攻城獅隊主場落腳竹縣體育館今天簽約 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3285195 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |work=自由時報 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128174501/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3285195 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林力仁的父親為泰雅族與貴州人混血，母親具有阿美族與台灣人血統<ref>{{cite news |author1=孫傳賢 |title=南山復仇 痛扁屏中 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/185082 |accessdate=2021-12-16 |work=自由時報 |date=2008-01-25 |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216045928/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/185082 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

